HEADWORD: Evenly
<hw>E"ven*ly</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>adv.</pos> <def>With an even,
level, or smooth surface; without roughness, elevations, or depression;
uniformly; equally; comfortably; impartially; serenely.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

